	('ab7ebe6b-78de-4574-8909-6e292bac7425', 'Celebrate Mother’s Day at the Louisville Zoo', 'Treat mom to a special day at the Zoo. In celebration of Mother’s Day, all mothers (and expecting mothers!) receive FREE Zoo admission on Sunday, May 10.  Spend the day exploring exhibits, watching animals enjoy the spring weather and making memories together as a family. From beloved animal moms to Zoo-wide experiences, there is something for everyone to enjoy.  How it works   Free admission is available to all mothers on Mother’s Day Tickets are available at the Zoo only Valid for standard daytime admission Zoo hours and regular parking fees apply.   Mother’s Day Specialty Drink  In honor of Mother’s Day Weekend, SSA will offer a special made‑to‑order Mother’s Day Mimosa, available for a limited time throughout the Zoo. This seasonal specialty is part of a new offering designed to give guests something a little different on select high‑traffic days. The Mother’s Day Mimosa will be available at multiple locations across the park for $10.99, while supplies last', '2026-05-10 14:00:00+00', '2026-05-10 21:00:00+00', 'America/New_York', 'Louisville Zoo', NULL, '4f546c98-7985-4127-b472-c43254eb77c3', 38.2051766, -85.7053359, NULL, NULL, NULL, true, 'https://louisvillezoo.org/event/celebrate-mothers-day-at-the-louisville-zoo/', 'Louisville Zoo Events', 'f0386301-e604-479b-bf96-7d55cb4662d5', '["https://louisvillezoo.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/PL_MothersDay.png"]', 'published', 0.833, NULL, false, 0, '''10'':36 ''10.99'':173 ''across'':169 ''admiss'':32,75,96 ''anim'':43,57 ''appli'':103 ''avail'':77,87,128,165 ''belov'':56 ''celebr'':1,19 ''day'':4,14,23,39,84,106,114,126,157,161 ''daytim'':95 ''design'':145 ''differ'':152 ''drink'':108 ''enjoy'':44,70 ''everyon'':68 ''exhibit'':41 ''expect'':27 ''experi'':63 ''explor'':40 ''famili'':54 ''fee'':102 ''free'':30,74 ''give'':147 ''guest'':148 ''high'':155 ''honor'':110 ''hour'':98 ''last'':176 ''limit'':131 ''littl'':151 ''locat''