	('f8ee646f-41ed-4b50-948f-48ecbcfb883e', 'Hump Day Happy Hour - Social Lights', 'buy now!  Doors open at 6:30 p.m.   Social Lights Let the good times GLOW!   Relax with a cool beverage and delicious appetizers while enjoying exclusive keeper talks and animal interactions in our Giraffe/Rhino area. As the sun sets, stay for our popular Wild Lights lantern festival.  Wild Lights entry is included with your Social Lights ticket. Guests will enjoy the happy hour experience first, then the full Wild Lights route will open at 8:00 p.m. You’ll have until 11:30 p.m. to explore the Zoo and take in the lanterns.  Tickets include event entry, tasty appetizers, and two drink tickets redeemable for beer, wine, or a specialty cocktail. Additional beverages will be available for purchase.        This event is for guests ages 21 and older. No children will be admitted. Outside alcohol will not be permitted.  There are no refunds, rainchecks or discounts for this special experience.  Ticket Prices  $50 per person  buy now!         21+ EVENTS        Trivia Night – Zooper Heroes March 18, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Join us for this green-themed trivia night and test your luck for a chance to win a pot of gold. (Actual prizes do not include real gold coins.)      Trivia Night – April Fools April 15, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Expect the unexpected! See what zany tricks we have up our sleeves at this punny and wacky night of trivia fun.     Monarchs and Mimosas – Spring 2026 (SOLD OUT) April 18, 2026 @ 8:30 am  Start your day with a refreshing cocktail as you learn how to create your own pollinator garden from our experts.     Trivia Night – Revenge of the Sixth May 6, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  May the facts be with you as you take on this galactic challenge. You could play Star Wars trivia Solo, but we recommend building a team of jedi masters. Seats may fill up in less than 12 parsecs, so do (or do not) reserve your seat early.     Hump Day Happy Hour – Social Lights May 20, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Let the good times GLOW! Relax with a cool beverage and delicious appetizers while enjoying exclusive keeper talks and animal interactions in our Giraffe/Rhino area.     Zoofari 2026 June 12, 2026 @ 6:00 pm  Join us in celebrating the 45th annual Zoofari gala hosted by Friends of the Louisville Zoo on Friday, June 12, 2026.      Trivia Night – Wild World of Disney June 17, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Put on your thinking cap (or favorite pair of Mickey ears) for this wild night of trivia. You’ll have to do more than wish upon a star to take the top prize.      Trivia Night – Spicy Summer Reads July 15, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Summer is heating up! Sparks will fly at this wild night of trivia based on book boyfriends from fan-favorite novels across all genres of romance.      Trivia Night – Mystery Flavor August 12, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  You can guess, but we won’t tell you! Join us for a wild night of trivia with a super-secret theme. Don’t worry—we promise it’s a good one.     Hump Day Happy Hour – Islands Getaway August 26, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Set you clock to Islands time! Relax with a cool beverage and delicious appetizers while enjoying exclusive keeper talks and animal interactions throughout our popular Islands exhibit area.     Trivia Night – Wild World of Disney September 2, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Put on your thinking cap (or favorite pair of Mickey ears) for this wild night of trivia. You’ll have to do more than wish upon a star to take the top prize.      Trivia Night – Cozy Caper November 18, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Only the greatest detectives will be able to solve the mystery. Answer trivia questions and put together clues to figure out ZOOdunnit.     Trivia Night – Jungle Bells December 16, 2026 @ 6:30 pm  Don your ugliest holiday sweater and test your knowledge for this wildly festive reindeer game.          ', '2026-05-20 22:30:00+00', '2026-05-21 00:30:00+00', 'America/New_York', 'Louisville Zoo', NULL, '4f546c98-7985-4127-b472-c43254eb77c3', 38.2051766, -85.7053359, 21, NULL, 50.00, false, 'https://louisvillezoo.or