	('6cb7f5a0-30c0-4ddb-b7b7-233578f3e535', 'Breakfast with the Beasts: Aldabra Tortoise', 'Buy Now! Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of the Aldabra Tortoise.  Wake up with some of your favorite animals in this program that brings a special look into how our animals start the day. Tickets include a hot breakfast featuring a waffle bar (Belgian waffles, assorted toppings, sausage links, fresh brewed coffee, orange juice and water), parking and admission for the day at the Zoo. Plus, the chance to ask all your questions to our knowledgeable staff! Breakfast will occur near the featured animals’ exhibit area and all programs will feature an exclusive keeper talk along with a chance to create enrichment for one of the Zoo’s animals!  Breakfast with the Beasts is intended for families with children ages 4 – 18.  Also good for scout and youth groups of the same age.  Prices $40 per person Age 2 and Under: $0 Advance purchase required.  Buy Now!           Breakfast with the Beasts Schedule        Breakfast with the Beasts: Beavers April 4, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of beavers.        Breakfast with the Beasts: Warthogs April 18, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of warthogs.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Zebra May 2, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of Zebra.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Aldabra Tortoise May 31, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of the Aldabra Tortoise.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Crocs and Gators June 13, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of Crocs and Gators.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Australia June 20, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of Australia.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Sumatran Tiger July 18, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of the Sumatran Tiger.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Giraffe August 8, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of Giraffes.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Orangutan August 15, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of Orangutans.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Aldabra Tortoise September 6, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of the Aldabra Tortoise.       Breakfast with the Beasts: Red Panda September 12, 2026 @ 9:00 am  Join us for Breakfast with the Beasts, where you’ll have the chance to enjoy a morning meal while observing and learning about the fascinating world of red pandas.               More Family Events       Looking for more Education Events and programs?  Learn more!', '2026-05-31 13:00:00+00', '2026-05-31 15:00:00+00', 'America/New_York', 'Zoo', NULL, '4f546c98-7985-4127-b472-c43254eb77c3', 38.2051766, -85.7053359, 4, 18, 40.00, false, 'https://loui