	('ca1da74c-3b71-4240-b70d-d8269ef2fa90', 'Super Summer Saturday (2026)', 'June 6, 2026 10 a.m. to 2 p.m. Free with Zoo Admission or your Louisville Membership  Pop! Bam! Wow! Fly, jump or warp your way over to the Zoo to visit with some of your favorite superheroes, here to kick off the summer season. While at the Zoo, learn about some of the amazing adaptations your favorite animals harness as their own wild “superpowers”.  Character meet and greets are FREE with Zoo admission or your Louisville Zoo Membership.   About Meet Me at the Zoo Imagination comes to life as kids (and kids-at-heart) meet some of their favorite characters from books, movies and more throughout the Zoo during this fun event series. Character meet and greets are FREE with Zoo admission or your Louisville Zoo Membership.  You’ll have multiple opportunities throughout the year to meet some of your favorite characters.  presented by          Meet Me at the Zoo        March 28 & 29 Bunny Hop Hop over for an EGGstra fun time as you meet the Easter Bunny, hunt for eggs and more.May 16 Storybook Character Day Your favorite characters hop straight off the page and into your Zoo. Meet Curious George, Pete the Cat and more!  June 6 Super Summer Saturday Fly, jump or warp your way over to the Zoo to visit with some of your favorite superheroes, here to kick off the summer season.  July 18 Summer Santa It’s a jolly summer holiday as Santa and Mrs. Claus stop at your Zoo while on vacation  August 8 Royal Rendezvous Join some of your favorite princesses as they close out the summer season with a special soiree at the Zoo.', '2026-06-06 14:00:00+00', '2026-06-06 18:00:00+00', 'America/New_York', 'Louisville Zoo, 1100 Trevilian Way, Louisville, KY, 40213, United States', 'Louisville Zoo, 1100 Trevilian Way, Louisville, KY, 40213, United States', '4f546c98-7985-4127-b472-c43254eb77c3', 38.2527000, -85.7585000, NULL, NULL, NULL, true, 'https://louisvillezoo.org/event/super-summer-saturday-2026/', 'Louisville Z